        {
            "title": "滙豐因聯邦快遞財報優於預期上調評級,受惠於收益率走強",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SkQIJ7ZR3rSz7htt9sydVw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPECBJ1C6_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 滙豐將<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯邦快遞\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯邦快遞;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯邦快遞\">聯邦快遞</a>(FedEx Corp)評級從減持上調至持有,此前該公司公布的第三季度業績優於預期,主要受核心快遞業務量和定價改善所推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商將目標價從335美元上調至360美元,並將2026至2028財年的盈利預測上調5-7%。<br/><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯邦快遞公布的2026財年第三季度非公認會計準則息稅前利潤(EBIT)年增7%,較預期高出16-17%,主要受惠於收益率上升6%,以及美國國內和國際出口貨運量的穩健增長。企業對企業(B2B)貨運量增長6%,國際出口增長2%。利潤率基本持平於6.7%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-87575a7f-e42f-3d4a-a921-0962993e617f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司亦上調了全年展望,預測營收增長6.0-6.5%,調整後每股盈利為19.30至20.10美元,高於先前預測區間。公司預計非公認會計準則息稅前利潤約為65億美元,反映快遞業務定價和需求趨勢走強。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐表示,收益率展望改善,特別是優先B2B貨運方面,是推動盈利超預期和上調指引的關鍵因素。該行預計這些趨勢將持續至第四季度,3月初的需求表現與第三季度的增長勢頭一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商表示,鑑於聯邦快遞在中東地區的業務敞口相對較低,中東衝突對其影響應保持有限,燃料成本部分被每週附加費調整所抵消。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐將息稅前利潤預測上調4-7%,並表示聯邦快遞定價環境改善對同業具有正面影響,包括聯合包裹服務公司(United Parcel Service Inc),而對德國郵政敦豪集團(Deutsche Post DHL Group)的影響則較為複雜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,該行指出,零擔貨運(less-than-truckload)業務的疲軟以及燃料和需求的不確定性可能限制進一步的上行空間,儘管該公司正推進計劃於6月分拆聯邦快遞貨運(FedEx Freight)業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%9B%A0%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E5%BF%AB%E9%81%9E%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%84%AA%E6%96%BC%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0%E6%96%BC%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E7%8E%87%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B7-165429804.html",
