        {
            "title": "滙豐上調雪佛龍及英國石油評級 中東衝擊推動盈利預測大幅上修",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F0m9iXdDFzAbivPD6Udegg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED9Q177_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 滙豐銀行對綜合石油板塊發布了多項評級及目標價上調,稱中東供應衝擊已引發2026年及2027年盈利預測的「大幅上修」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資深分析師Kim Fustier表示,該行現將雪佛龍(Chevron)上調至買入評級,將英國石油(<span><span>BP</span></span>)上調至持有評級,並將Galp下調至持有評級,同時對埃尼集團(ENI)、挪威國家石油(<span><span>Equinor</span></span>)、雷普索爾(Repsol)、殼牌(<span><span>Shell</span></span>)、道達爾能源(TotalEnergies)及埃克森美孚(ExxonMobil)維持中性或謹慎立場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eff5a4cd-bebd-3e4d-8468-829d9e3e3907-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整體目標價平均上調22%,其中<span><span>英國石油</span></span>目標價上調至565便士,<span><span>雪佛龍</span></span>上調至215美元,埃克森美孚上調至158美元,<span><span>殼牌</span></span>上調至3,350便士,道達爾能源上調至77歐元,Galp上調至21歐元,西方石油上調至68美元,埃尼集團上調至21歐元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐指出,自2月28日以來霍爾木茲海峽實際關閉,已對石油、煉油及液化天然氣市場造成「前所未有的實體供應中斷」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行大幅上調2026年宏觀假設,將布蘭特原油價格從65美元上調至每桶80美元,歐洲TTF天然氣價格從10美元上調至14美元/百萬英熱單位,煉油利潤率上調50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管許多石油巨頭因區域曝險而面臨產量損失,滙豐表示這「被更高的油氣價格所抵消有餘」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對中東曝險有限的公司,如<span><span>挪威國家石油</span></span>、<span><span>雷普索爾</span></span>及埃尼集團,股價漲幅最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐現將2026年盈利預測平均上調50%,2027年預測上調13%,其中對石油敏感度高的英國石油及雪佛龍、煉油商如雷普索爾,以及天然氣曝險較高的挪威國家石油上調幅度最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此,滙豐警告估值「看起來大致合理」,股價已接近歷史高位,但強勁的大宗商品動能「很可能推動股價進一步上漲」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E9%9B%AA%E4%BD%9B%E9%BE%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE-154521481.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 00:02:21",
